Text: This is the install CD for the Datel Trash Talker, a piece of hardware that can store audio files for playing over XboxLive. This is an important part of the product as it contains the drivers for it, which allows you to transfer audio to and from the device. I uploaded this, because if you lose the CD that came with the device, then you're fucked. So now, if you lose your CD (like I did) you can download this.
